                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <div id="videos">
                    <div class="video-link-wrapper">
                        <a href="#" class="video-link" id="videoLink" target="_blank">
                            <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                            <span id="videoLinkText">Loading video link...</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
